    format("I know that things are a little haywire right now, but…\p The rocket launched safely! That's successful launch no. {STR_VAR_1}!")
}

text MossdeepCity_SpaceCenter_1F_Text_RocketLaunchDemandsPerfection {
    format("A rocket launch demands perfection. Not even a 1% margin of error is allowed.\p Even if it's 99% okay, the whole thing is useless if 1% happens to be no good.\p Despite that, we never stop trying. Why? It's a dream that never ends.")
}

text MossdeepCity_SpaceCenter_1F_Text_MagmaHaveSightsOnSpaceCenter {
    format("Those MAGMA thugs have their sights set on our SPACE CENTER.\p But we can't allow anything that minor to interfere with our rocket launch!")
}

text MossdeepCity_SpaceCenter_1F_Text_FoundThisYouCanHaveIt {
    format("I was taking a stroll down the beach when I found this.\p It's not anything I need, so you can have it.")
}

text MossdeepCity_SpaceCenter_1F_Text_HoennFamousForMeteorShowers {
    format("The HOENN region has been famous for its meteor showers for a long time.")
}

text MossdeepCity_SpaceCenter_1F_Text_MagmaCantStealFuelTakeThis {
    format("TEAM MAGMA can't be allowed to steal the rocket fuel.\p Oh, by the way, you can have this stone I found on the beach.")
}

text MossdeepCity_SpaceCenter_1F_Text_CantStrollOnBeachWithMagma {
    format("With TEAM MAGMA around, I guess strolls on the beach aren't safe.")
}

text MossdeepCity_SpaceCenter_1F_Text_DidPokemonComeFromSpace {
    format("Some people claim that POKéMON came from space. Could it be true?")
}

text MossdeepCity_SpaceCenter_1F_Text_AquaShouldBeatMagma {
    format("TEAM AQUA should take care of TEAM MAGMA!\p But if they did that, TEAM AQUA will become bold and brazen, won't they?")
}

text MossdeepCity_SpaceCenter_1F_Text_RocketsBoggleMyMind {
    format("A giant chunk of metal bursts through the skies and flies into space…\p It boggles my mind!")
}

text MossdeepCity_SpaceCenter_1F_Text_MagmaWantsToSpoilMyDream {
    format("A giant chunk of metal bursts through the skies and flies into space…\p But TEAM MAGMA wants to spoil that dream of mine!\p I'm not having any of that!")
}

text MossdeepCity_SpaceCenter_1F_Text_StevenMagmaCantBeAllowedToTakeFuel {
    format("STEVEN: {PLAYER}{KUN}, have you read that proclamation already?\p TEAM MAGMA is coming after the rocket fuel on this island.\p I don't know what they'd need it for, but they can't be allowed to take it.\p I'll keep an eye on things for a while longer.\p In the meantime, why don't you go check out the town?")
}

text MossdeepCity_SpaceCenter_1F_Text_Grunt3Intro {
    format("As promised, we've come for the rocket fuel!")
}

text MossdeepCity_SpaceCenter_1F_Text_Grunt3Defeat {
